queries_executed.name: All_Transporter_Nodes
queries_executed.query:
MATCH (t:Transporter)
                RETURN 
                    t.name as name,
                    t.epa_id as epa_id,
                    t.address as address,
                    t.city as city,
                    t.state as state,
                    t.license_number as license_number,
                    properties(t) as all_properties
                ORDER BY t.name
